What? Say that again

819
01:04:18,921 --> 01:04:19,843
Good evening

820
01:04:23,670 --> 01:04:27,522
Ah, were you back? Thank you for your hard work

821
01:04:27,812 --> 01:04:29,624
Are you Tsuyoshi's mother?

822
01:04:29,649 --> 01:04:31,288
I wonder if he is doing well

823
01:04:31,313 --> 01:04:33,131
I called, but I couldn't meet him because he was busy

824
01:04:33,589 --> 01:04:34,853
He seems to be doing well.

825
01:04:34,878 --> 01:04:43,233
Is that so? I just wanted to give this
little bit to you, teacher, for you to eat

826
01:04:45,656 --> 01:04:47,045
Oh, thank you.

827
01:04:47,690 --> 01:04:49,945
This is a nice color

828
01:04:50,300 --> 01:04:51,536
You used to like this too

829
01:04:52,380 --> 01:04:54,139
If that's the case, I just chilled it a bit

830
01:05:02,255 --> 01:05:05,255
You guys get along well.

831
01:05:32,937 --> 01:05:35,485
Just because your friend got license

832
01:05:35,510 --> 01:05:37,527
why do you have to be the one to get a ride?

833
01:05:41,615 --> 01:05:43,762
You are in a privileged position, after all

834
01:05:46,260 --> 01:05:49,260
You really need to understand that part well

835
01:05:49,630 --> 01:05:52,656
Well, there's nothing
we can do about it today,

836
01:05:52,763 --> 01:05:54,283
Thank you very much.

837
01:06:21,598 --> 01:06:23,320
Oh

838
01:06:26,032 --> 01:06:27,096
what did you come here for?

839
01:06:27,763 --> 01:06:30,285
I came to see you

840
01:06:31,022 --> 01:06:35,137
The women's association in the village decided to inspect the stadium,

841
01:06:35,600 --> 01:06:37,476
and I was chosen as the representative to come

842
01:06:37,500 --> 01:06:40,326
and help with the construction of the stadium

843
01:06:40,350 --> 01:06:43,350
I'm glad it's a big factory

844
01:06:44,010 --> 01:06:48,067
Mr. Tsukamoto is such a kind person

845
01:06:49,050 --> 01:06:50,886
Everyone just dispersed a little while ago

846
01:06:50,910 --> 01:06:53,486
I'm going home on the train this evening

847
01:06:53,510 --> 01:06:57,059
They said you can't come because we're busy during the day

848
01:06:57,084 --> 01:07:00,084
You're going to the night school, right?

849
01:07:00,532 --> 01:07:03,532
We are not going to night school

850
01:07:04,509 --> 01:07:06,025
This is our pamphlet

851
01:07:06,670 --> 01:07:07,900
Thank you for your reference

852
01:07:08,103 --> 01:07:10,669
Hey, you all, I'm going to give you a break from now on

853
01:07:10,700 --> 01:07:12,039
why don't you try talking her somewhere?

854
01:07:12,401 --> 01:07:15,400
it would be nice if you could make a great sightseeing in Tokyo  with the kids

855
01:07:15,960 --> 01:07:18,916
If I can see their cheerful faces,

856
01:07:19,225 --> 01:07:21,365
then I can talk to everyone

857
01:07:21,430 --> 01:07:22,486
Change your clothes.

858
01:07:23,263 --> 01:07:24,706
Thank you very much.

859
01:07:25,207 --> 01:07:26,847
Let's get ready.

860
01:07:27,690 --> 01:07:29,134
Please wait a moment

861
01:07:49,749 --> 01:07:50,916
4 cold noodles.

862
01:07:51,097 --> 01:07:52,410
4 cold noodles.

863
01:07:55,593 --> 01:07:57,592
Oh, you came!

864
01:07:58,888 --> 01:08:01,262
Auntie, you came here well,

865
01:08:01,287 --> 01:08:03,433
You've grown up

866
01:08:03,987 --> 01:08:06,356
Since you are here, They let me have a break

867
01:08:06,380 --> 01:08:07,518
I want to eat quickly.

868
01:08:07,549 --> 01:08:09,743
What, you haven't ordered yet?

869
01:08:09,840 --> 01:08:11,513
We've been waiting until you got back

870
01:08:11,730 --> 01:08:14,730
Alright, I'll have whatever you want to order

871
01:08:14,755 --> 01:08:16,876
Thanks for treating us

872
01:08:16,983 --> 01:08:19,065
In exchange, say everyone

873
01:08:19,223 --> 01:08:20,951
You had something delicious at my place

874
01:08:21,456 --> 01:08:22,356
What do you want?

875
01:08:22,530 --> 01:08:24,016
It's already decided that we're having tempura rice bowl

876
01:08:24,047 --> 01:08:26,090
Alright, three tempura rice bowls.

877
01:08:26,218 --> 01:08:27,555
Yes, three tempura rice bowls

878
01:08:27,580 --> 01:08:29,267
It'll be ready soon,

879
01:08:31,726 --> 01:08:33,333
Hey look.

880
01:08:34,030 --> 01:08:35,683
Isn't that Tsuyoshi?

881
01:08:40,985 --> 01:08:41,885
That's amazing,

882
01:08:41,986 --> 01:08:43,593
He passed the exam in one go!

883
01:08:44,009 --> 01:08:45,660
Oh, you got your driver's license?

884
01:08:45,774 --> 01:08:46,494
That's great!

885
01:08:46,590 --> 01:08:47,636
I'm going to practice today

886
01:08:49,856 --> 01:08:52,475
Are you going for date?

887
01:08:52,500 --> 01:08:53,747
That's great!

888
01:08:55,480 --> 01:08:56,886
What's up with Minoru?

889
01:08:56,910 --> 01:08:59,910
He has been sleeping for about a week because of his bronchitis

890
01:09:00,358 --> 01:09:01,845
That's a chest ailment.

891
01:09:02,477 --> 01:09:03,912
but it's not serious case.

892
01:09:04,380 --> 01:09:07,380
That guy isn't strong.

893
01:09:09,930 --> 01:09:10,750
so should we visit him?

894
01:09:11,264 --> 01:09:12,537
No, no, don't do that

895
01:09:13,305 --> 01:09:13,992
Why not?

896
01:09:15,076 --> 01:09:16,823
It would be a problem if everyone know

897
01:09:18,771 --> 01:09:21,412
Oh it's time to work.

898
01:09:21,780 --> 01:09:23,107
I see

899
01:09:23,132 --> 01:09:25,693
 well then, see you next time.

900
01:09:38,893 --> 01:09:41,893
See you again, goodbye.

901
01:10:50,651 --> 01:10:51,997
I’m sorry.

902
01:11:19,560 --> 01:11:21,021
This is the smell of grass.

903
01:11:31,529 --> 01:11:32,740
This is the smell of sea.

904
01:11:37,737 --> 01:11:38,979
kayo-chan?

905
01:11:43,570 --> 01:11:46,570
I'm a fine mechanic

906
01:11:47,770 --> 01:11:52,404
A fine mechanic must know everything about cars

907
01:11:53,140 --> 01:11:57,857
I feel like I want to dive into the engine and become gasoline for a moment

908
01:11:58,810 --> 01:11:59,926
Don't rush it

909
01:11:59,950 --> 01:12:01,786
You have to graduate one step at a time,

910
01:12:02,380 --> 01:12:04,357
but you've completed an important stage

911
01:12:04,940 --> 01:12:06,505
You got your driver's license, right?

912
01:12:09,689 --> 01:12:12,255
You're going to be a nurse?

913
01:12:12,280 --> 01:12:14,708
I still have a long way to go.

914
01:12:14,737 --> 01:12:16,863
whenever I think about studying, I get sleepy

915
01:12:17,700 --> 01:12:21,958
I'm going to become independent and take charge around 30.

916
01:12:22,885 --> 01:12:24,281
You're a hard worker,

917
01:12:24,360 --> 01:12:26,169
so I'm sure you will make it.

918
01:12:26,852 --> 01:12:29,852
You have to get a bride first, right?

919
01:12:30,870 --> 01:12:32,154
A bride?

920
01:13:22,951 --> 01:13:24,245
I'm home.

921
01:13:25,850 --> 01:13:27,136
What have you been doing until now?

922
01:13:27,161 --> 01:13:27,870
You have a customer, right?

923
01:13:31,533 --> 01:13:32,833
Yuko.

924
01:13:33,100 --> 01:13:36,536
What happened to you,

925
01:13:36,942 --> 01:13:38,416
The factory went bankrupt.

926
01:13:41,172 --> 01:13:43,314
Oh, is that so? What about Aki chan and others.

927
01:13:43,610 --> 01:13:45,756
Akichan and Masachan are going to work in Hamamatsu

928
01:13:45,780 --> 01:13:47,475
They went to a coffee shop,

929
01:13:48,019 --> 01:13:50,867
Kacchan ended up becoming a service girl at a hotel in Osaka

930
01:13:53,503 --> 01:13:57,677
I thought there might be something in Tokyo, so I came out here

931
01:14:00,930 --> 01:14:02,496
Until I find a job

932
01:14:02,520 --> 01:14:03,826
Can you let me stay as maid here?

933
01:14:04,934 --> 01:14:06,125
It's fine to be free of charge

934
01:14:06,760 --> 01:14:08,729
Try asking the wife.

935
01:14:17,830 --> 01:14:18,437
See you

936
01:14:18,797 --> 01:14:20,166
Buy a medicine and come back

937
01:14:41,839 --> 01:14:42,628
What's wrong?

938
01:14:42,660 --> 01:14:44,436
The truck we repaired yesterday got stuck in the river with the steel materials still loaded

939
01:14:44,460 --> 01:14:46,836
It got stuck in the river with
the steel materials still on board

940
01:14:46,860 --> 01:14:48,539
They say it's our repair fault, you know

941
01:14:49,400 --> 01:14:51,086
Three people died,

942
01:15:02,038 --> 01:15:04,367
Sorry to keep you waiting.

943
01:15:06,664 --> 01:15:09,664
There's nothing wrong.

944
01:15:12,258 --> 01:15:13,306
You should drive us there

945
01:15:13,860 --> 01:15:16,330
Please, go ahead and get in

946
01:15:16,532 --> 01:15:17,594
Don't worry about it

947
01:15:32,551 --> 01:15:35,551
Today's work is finished

948
01:15:51,591 --> 01:15:53,305
Shall we head home?

949
01:15:55,915 --> 01:15:57,462
Tsuyoshi.

950
01:16:03,587 --> 01:16:04,798
Do you want to drink tea?

951
01:16:05,022 --> 01:16:06,360
Just wait a moment.

952
01:16:06,987 --> 01:16:09,625
there's no point in worrying about it now,

953
01:16:09,912 --> 01:16:11,448
so let's have a drink of shochu to lighten the mood

954
01:16:11,473 --> 01:16:12,911
This is quite nice, isn't it?

955
01:16:12,935 --> 01:16:14,473
Come on, let's not do that

956
01:16:17,210 --> 01:16:20,210
But, isn't there anything we can do while we still have time?

957
01:16:20,410 --> 01:16:22,352
It's nothing serious, really

958
01:16:24,610 --> 01:16:27,036
This place isn't going to collapse, right?

959
01:16:27,060 --> 01:16:29,000
Don't say such bad luck things

960
01:16:29,910 --> 01:16:32,910
But we might have to pay damages, right?

961
01:16:34,070 --> 01:16:37,852
We haven't had an accident like this until today

962
01:16:38,672 --> 01:16:43,206
However, working two nights straight
like this is such an unreasonable task

963
01:16:43,230 --> 01:16:47,742
If we did the same as other factories, they would take our jobs.

964
01:16:48,680 --> 01:16:50,641
Well, that's true, but...

965
01:16:51,769 --> 01:16:54,655
So, Tsuyoshi, do you want a drink?

966
01:16:54,680 --> 01:16:56,055
I'm fine.

967
01:17:00,438 --> 01:17:02,566
I'm really sorry about this, you know

968
01:17:02,591 --> 01:17:03,755
Hurry up.

969
01:17:04,784 --> 01:17:06,594
Thank you very much.

970
01:17:07,219 --> 01:17:10,219
I'm sorry for making everyone take a break

971
01:17:10,500 --> 01:17:11,526
Thank you for your work.

972
01:17:11,604 --> 01:17:15,062
I will let everyone know about your achievements.

973
01:17:18,578 --> 01:17:20,341
so take care and stay healthy

974
01:17:20,420 --> 01:17:22,156
Make sure to work hard!

975
01:17:22,180 --> 01:17:25,180
and studying hard.

976
01:17:26,938 --> 01:17:28,235
Thank you very much.

977
01:17:39,772 --> 01:17:40,719
Sorry.

978
01:17:44,686 --> 01:17:47,686
She thought we'd been to night school.

979
01:17:48,879 --> 01:17:51,320
I really thought I should tell the truth

980
01:17:51,814 --> 01:17:53,367
but it's better to stay quiet

981
01:17:55,863 --> 01:17:57,003
I feel hot.

982
01:17:59,331 --> 01:18:00,985
You don't go to the night school but

983
01:18:01,010 --> 01:18:03,116
Why you wear high school uniform?

984
01:18:03,140 --> 01:18:03,836
Is this it?

985
01:18:03,860 --> 01:18:05,326
 You're pushing yourself,

986
01:18:05,350 --> 01:18:07,266
I like to wear this.

987
01:18:07,290 --> 01:18:08,696
I've always wanted to wear this.

988
01:18:08,720 --> 01:18:11,720
Don't dress up so extravagantly.

989
01:18:11,745 --> 01:18:13,418
You guys shouldn't be whining either.

990
01:18:14,126 --> 01:18:17,126
I'm not going to cry or whine

991
01:18:19,692 --> 01:18:21,045
even if I can't study

992
01:18:21,720 --> 01:18:23,295
I'm going to become a respectable person

993
01:18:32,440 --> 01:18:34,366
If such a big newspaper comes out,

994
01:18:34,390 --> 01:18:36,620
trust will take a hit

995
01:18:37,750 --> 01:18:40,750
It’s written as if we dropped the truck ourselves

996
01:18:49,470 --> 01:18:52,470
You know, I’ve been thinking about it

997
01:18:53,029 --> 01:18:54,895
If it's the boss's responsibility, the commotion will get bigger

998
01:18:54,920 --> 01:18:57,756
Well, what if this guy runs to the police?

999
01:18:57,781 --> 01:18:59,349
What do you mean?

1000
01:18:59,682 --> 01:19:02,246
If we say it's just a rookie's mistake,
the penalty will be lighter

1001
01:19:02,270 --> 01:19:07,041
On that day, I was removing rust from another car

1002
01:19:08,110 --> 01:19:09,697
I know that already

1003
01:19:10,939 --> 01:19:14,412
Do you hate to save this factory?

1004
01:19:17,443 --> 01:19:19,410
Can you go to the police?

1005
01:19:20,840 --> 01:19:23,396
that might be a good idea

1006
01:19:23,421 --> 01:19:24,746
This is the time

1007
01:19:24,770 --> 01:19:26,212
It's time to repay the favor to boss.

1008
01:19:29,027 --> 01:19:29,907
Wife.

1009
01:19:32,324 --> 01:19:33,370
What's going on?

1010
01:19:34,080 --> 01:19:36,486
I've been asking on them until now

1011
01:19:36,510 --> 01:19:38,576
It seems that we will have to cover half of the expenses

1012
01:19:38,600 --> 01:19:39,965
That's terrible.

1013
01:19:40,139 --> 01:19:41,559
when is boss coming back?

1014
01:19:41,584 --> 01:19:43,792
I heard he might be back tonight.

1015
01:19:44,060 --> 01:19:47,992
It seems that the compensation for the three deceased will be covered by Yamashita Construction,

1016
01:19:48,113 --> 01:19:50,229
but we will have to cover the truck's compensation

1017
01:19:50,254 --> 01:19:51,964
It's really troubling

1018
01:19:52,498 --> 01:19:54,418
it's not a small amount of money.

1019
01:19:55,160 --> 01:19:59,240
So, I have a favor to ask you

1020
01:19:59,951 --> 01:20:02,897
It's about your month's salary

1021
01:20:02,941 --> 01:20:06,884
Wife, I actually have a good idea

1022
01:20:08,080 --> 01:20:10,015
It was decided that we would sacrifice one victim

1023
01:20:11,470 --> 01:20:12,734
What does that mean?

1024
01:20:45,953 --> 01:20:47,712
Do you need something?

1025
01:20:48,594 --> 01:20:51,500
Ah, I'm from the Tsuyama Auto Repair Shop

1026
01:20:51,623 --> 01:20:55,914
Tsuyama? Oh, the repair shop for the truck that got stuck in the river?

1027
01:20:56,680 --> 01:20:58,383
The issue was just finished

1028
01:20:59,050 --> 01:21:02,707
The master is eating at the eel shop behind with the truck right now

1029
01:21:03,290 --> 01:21:06,290
Don't worry, he'll be heading back around here

1030
01:21:12,502 --> 01:21:15,502
What are the factory saying about?

1031
01:21:15,910 --> 01:21:18,910
They say to cut the salary in half for the time being

1032
01:21:19,490 --> 01:21:22,086
Since the accident, we haven't had any work at all

1033
01:21:22,110 --> 01:21:25,110
I'm in trouble with half my salary.

1034
01:21:26,606 --> 01:21:28,879
I've been sending half of it to my family every month

1035
01:21:30,420 --> 01:21:33,420
Starting next year, my younger brother will be going to school,

1036
01:21:33,540 --> 01:21:35,718
why quit and look for something else?

1037
01:21:36,464 --> 01:21:38,941
But I still want to do car repairs.

1038
01:21:39,295 --> 01:21:40,962
aren't there any other repair shops?

1039
01:21:43,202 --> 01:21:44,916
There's no job opening.

1040
01:21:48,130 --> 01:21:49,543
See you later

1041
01:21:56,095 --> 01:21:56,948
How are you?

1042
01:21:58,187 --> 01:21:59,535
Have you seen a doctor?

1043
01:22:03,892 --> 01:22:07,274
Yeah, go buy some eggs with this

1044
01:22:07,540 --> 01:22:08,233
Don't worry.

1045
01:22:08,559 --> 01:22:09,625
You're in trouble

1046
01:22:09,650 --> 01:22:11,716
 I'm just physically strong

1047
01:22:11,740 --> 01:22:13,286
Even if things get a little tough, it'll work out somehow

1048
01:22:18,093 --> 01:22:19,547
Well, thank you

1049
01:22:20,147 --> 01:22:21,054
 it's all good

1050
01:22:21,270 --> 01:22:22,271
We're in this together

1051
01:22:22,875 --> 01:22:24,795
Ah, it's raining

1052
01:22:25,968 --> 01:22:26,915
Oh my god.

1053
01:22:27,680 --> 01:22:29,776
Take my umbrella.

1054
01:23:06,836 --> 01:23:09,277
It's unavoidable for now,

1055
01:23:09,690 --> 01:23:12,690
but please look for other good places eventually

1056
01:23:12,820 --> 01:23:17,569
Well, as long as the person is reliable, it doesn't matter where she works.

1057
01:23:18,490 --> 01:23:21,187
Thank you for everything.

1058
01:23:21,340 --> 01:23:22,974
Alright, let's go.

1059
01:23:24,033 --> 01:23:26,080
It's a nice place you live in

1060
01:23:26,690 --> 01:23:28,769
What a lovely kitchen!

1061
01:23:32,655 --> 01:23:34,535
If anything comes up, just give me a call, okay?

1062
01:23:34,841 --> 01:23:35,587
Kae?

1063
01:23:36,454 --> 01:23:38,507
You forgot something again

1064
01:23:38,555 --> 01:23:39,462
Sorry.

1065
01:23:39,917 --> 01:23:41,130
See you.

1066
01:23:43,751 --> 01:23:45,285
So you're going again, huh?

1067
01:23:45,310 --> 01:23:46,050
Yes.

1068
01:23:47,176 --> 01:23:49,239
Thank you for your help.

1069
01:23:50,829 --> 01:23:51,603
Take care.

1070
01:24:00,309 --> 01:24:01,619
Yuko

1071
01:24:25,923 --> 01:24:26,990
Here it is.

1072
01:24:28,659 --> 01:24:33,758
I'll take the first
month's salary as a thank you, okay?

1073
01:24:33,859 --> 01:24:34,525
Yes.

1074
01:24:36,505 --> 01:24:38,660
Excuse me, may I come in?

1075
01:24:45,868 --> 01:24:47,364
Come in.

1076
01:25:06,681 --> 01:25:08,173
Hey Tsuyoshi.

1077
01:25:12,350 --> 01:25:13,915
You come over here, okay?

1078
01:25:14,603 --> 01:25:15,384
Yes.

1079
01:25:19,700 --> 01:25:22,700
Well, you have to stop

1080
01:25:23,000 --> 01:25:25,536
Is this factory going to shut down?

1081
01:25:25,560 --> 01:25:27,439
There's nothing we can do about this

1082
01:25:28,200 --> 01:25:30,376
We suddenly lost my job.

1083
01:25:30,400 --> 01:25:31,956
I had to compensate a huge amount of money for the truck

1084
01:25:33,025 --> 01:25:34,980
So what are we supposed to do from now on?

1085
01:25:35,190 --> 01:25:37,087
If you say that, I can't really say....

1086
01:25:37,980 --> 01:25:38,786
but you guys too...

1087
01:25:38,810 --> 01:25:41,429
It's no use just sticking
around here forever.

1088
01:25:41,454 --> 01:25:42,367
what are you going to do, boss?

1089
01:25:44,765 --> 01:25:49,359
I think we could buy at least one new
souvenir truck instead of this rundown factory

1090
01:25:50,950 --> 01:25:57,187
With that, I think we could do some work for a transport
company and get back to a point where we can own a factory again

1091
01:25:59,170 --> 01:26:02,170
So, will you come back again

1092
01:26:02,410 --> 01:26:04,826
Boss?

1093
01:26:04,850 --> 01:26:07,850
Isn't there any way to keep this factory running?

1094
01:26:08,160 --> 01:26:08,816
Even if you say that...

1095
01:26:08,840 --> 01:26:11,840
Aren't you the one saying this?

1096
01:26:13,200 --> 01:26:15,246
I have nowhere to go anyway

1097
01:26:15,270 --> 01:26:16,936
I'll work for free a little,

1098
01:26:16,960 --> 01:26:18,956
so please give me a job

1099
01:26:18,980 --> 01:26:21,746
Don't say anything to me anymore

1100
01:26:21,770 --> 01:26:24,666
I've run out of my evening drink

1101
01:26:24,690 --> 01:26:28,627
It's quite a mystery that such a small factory has managed to survive until now,

1102
01:26:28,905 --> 01:26:29,998
But.

1103
01:26:30,378 --> 01:26:32,321
come on, there's no helping it

1104
01:26:33,148 --> 01:26:34,408
It can't be helped.

1105
01:26:40,792 --> 01:26:42,043
Oh, someone is coming

1106
01:26:42,557 --> 01:26:43,365
For you, right?

1107
01:26:52,000 --> 01:26:55,000
What's wrong? Do you need something?

1108
01:27:18,018 --> 01:27:19,456
Are you in Nagoya?

1109
01:27:27,954 --> 01:27:30,954
you're really far away, huh?

1110
01:27:31,320 --> 01:27:34,320
I thought there wouldn't be any jobs in Tokyo,

1111
01:27:35,170 --> 01:27:38,170
so I looked around, but all I found were jobs as hostesses at cabarets or maids at hot springs

1112
01:27:39,379 --> 01:27:44,885
I don't really want to do that, but since I quit the hospital and decided to move, I thought I'd go along with it

1113
01:27:46,970 --> 01:27:49,970
The person they call their late brother from Nagoya

1114
01:27:50,552 --> 01:27:51,948
So he really was a doctor

1115
01:27:51,980 --> 01:27:54,980
I heard it's a big hospital

1116
01:27:55,780 --> 01:27:58,780
It seems that our teacher will take over from there

1117
01:27:59,579 --> 01:28:00,795
When are you going?

1118
01:28:00,820 --> 01:28:01,725
it's soon.

1119
01:28:05,200 --> 01:28:08,478
then I guess I won't be able to see you

1120
01:28:08,736 --> 01:28:12,543
I can't even take a break to come back once a month.

1121
01:28:13,987 --> 01:28:14,814
It's hard.

1122
01:28:20,136 --> 01:28:23,626
What will happen
to your factory?

1123
01:28:23,650 --> 01:28:24,548
I have no idea

1124
01:28:29,150 --> 01:28:33,308
I sometimes write letters, so give me some too, okay?

1125
01:28:34,830 --> 01:28:37,830
Yeah, I promise,

1126
01:28:39,098 --> 01:28:40,205
Definitely.

1127
01:29:29,074 --> 01:29:30,300
Teacher.

1128
01:29:30,724 --> 01:29:32,444
Inoue teacher.

1129
01:29:35,399 --> 01:29:38,399
Please be quiet, I can't study

1130
01:29:39,750 --> 01:29:40,754
What?

1131
01:29:42,181 --> 01:29:44,327
Everyone, calm down!

1132
01:29:46,051 --> 01:29:46,691
What's going on?

1133
01:29:46,899 --> 01:29:49,115
It's so noisy that I can't study
for our entrance exams

1134
01:29:49,140 --> 01:29:50,426
Could you please be a little quieter?

1135
01:29:50,451 --> 01:29:51,473
Who said that?

1136
01:29:51,856 --> 01:29:52,864
Miura teacher.

1137
01:30:04,800 --> 01:30:09,002
Please value students who are working as well as students who are going on to higher education.

1138
01:30:12,898 --> 01:30:16,722
There are many people here who work after graduating from junior high school.

1139
01:30:17,573 --> 01:30:21,293
In the future, when you enter society, it's all good

1140
01:30:27,216 --> 01:30:30,518
Now, everyone, please begin.

1141
01:30:52,569 --> 01:30:53,582
Welcome back.

1142
01:30:53,940 --> 01:30:55,133
It must have been cold.

1143
01:31:00,091 --> 01:31:01,804
It's snowing

1144
01:31:02,322 --> 01:31:03,975
I'm cooking now.

1145
01:31:29,222 --> 01:31:30,209
What's wrong?

1146
01:31:35,183 --> 01:31:38,200
Children who got jobs must be having a hard time like this

1147
01:31:41,940 --> 01:31:45,083
I received a letter from Arai who work at hospital

1148
01:31:50,325 --> 01:31:52,755
She's going to Nagoya with her master.

1149
01:31:52,780 --> 01:31:53,684
Really?

1150
01:31:57,507 --> 01:31:59,580
It seems Yuko has also
become an assistant at the inn

1151
01:32:08,650 --> 01:32:11,179
Tsuyoshi's repair shop is something wrong.

1152
01:32:13,052 --> 01:32:18,862
it feels like just yesterday
when everyone left with their hopes high.

1153
01:32:25,336 --> 01:32:30,499
The places where junior high school graduates get jobs are all just barely making ends meet

1154
01:32:32,530 --> 01:32:35,530
They say that when a department store opens in Fukushima,

1155
01:32:35,920 --> 01:32:38,920
it causes a lot of retail businesses to collapse

1156
01:32:40,399 --> 01:32:42,266
What will Tsuyoshi do?

1157
01:32:50,528 --> 01:32:51,967
Are you going out?

1158
01:32:53,574 --> 01:32:54,567
I'll go to Tsuyoshi's place.

1159
01:32:54,929 --> 01:32:56,995
I heard that mom is sick, so I think I'll go visit her

1160
01:32:57,540 --> 01:32:58,996
Make sure to eat your meal first

1161
01:32:59,020 --> 01:33:01,667
I come back right

1162
01:33:04,080 --> 01:33:09,849
Aren't you going to eat anymore? The doctor said you should eat more.

1163
01:33:12,890 --> 01:33:14,734
Good evening, teacher

1164
01:33:15,886 --> 01:33:17,612
Good evening

1165
01:33:18,450 --> 01:33:21,246
I wonder how she is.

1166
01:33:21,270 --> 01:33:24,270
Her sickness haven't recovered for a long time

1167
01:33:24,759 --> 01:33:26,099
I wonder if Tsuyoshi-kun
will send a letter.

1168
01:33:26,204 --> 01:33:28,352
he hasn't said anything lately

1169
01:33:28,580 --> 01:33:29,727
Come in.

1170
01:33:32,895 --> 01:33:34,725
Tsuyoshi's teacher is here.

1171
01:33:38,660 --> 01:33:41,028
Ah, you have to sleep,
you can't be awake

1172
01:33:42,600 --> 01:33:45,600
That guy, Go-sensei

1173
01:33:46,279 --> 01:33:48,635
It's been nothing from Tsuyoshi lately

1174
01:33:48,660 --> 01:33:51,466
He can't really say anything about it

1175
01:33:51,490 --> 01:33:53,313
I wonder if something happened

1176
01:33:53,778 --> 01:33:55,519
He must be busy.

1177
01:33:56,736 --> 01:33:59,162
I think he's fine.

1178
01:33:59,935 --> 01:34:01,525
Don't worry.

1179
01:34:02,711 --> 01:34:03,490
Bring the tea.

1180
01:34:04,209 --> 01:34:05,165
It's fine, it's fine, I'm sorry

1181
01:34:06,490 --> 01:34:08,337
Excuse me.

1182
01:35:05,658 --> 01:35:06,814
How was it?

1183
01:35:07,306 --> 01:35:09,776
The director had been saying for a while that I should go breathe some fresh country air

1184
01:35:13,087 --> 01:35:14,747
The director said like that.

1185
01:35:16,660 --> 01:35:19,660
Speaking of Minoru Obara,

1186
01:35:20,050 --> 01:35:21,897
The doctor says it's quite serious

1187
01:35:22,140 --> 01:35:23,899
We are thinking of sending him back to the countryside

1188
01:35:24,494 --> 01:35:25,508
Will you fire him?

1189
01:35:25,810 --> 01:35:27,764
I'll use him again once he's better

1190
01:35:28,300 --> 01:35:30,761
But I don't think he will be better for a while

1191
01:35:30,940 --> 01:35:32,425
It's not about the retirement bonus

1192
01:35:32,610 --> 01:35:33,706
If he lose his job,

1193
01:35:33,744 --> 01:35:35,805
he will be discouraging.

1194
01:35:35,830 --> 01:35:38,096
So, I thought I would use one of them

1195
01:35:38,120 --> 01:35:39,550
since they had been asking me for a while

1196
01:35:40,080 --> 01:35:42,196
Oh, what was your friend's name again?

1197
01:35:42,220 --> 01:35:43,266
Is it Nishiyama-kun?

1198
01:35:43,290 --> 01:35:44,996
Hmm, is he still over there?

1199
01:35:45,020 --> 01:35:47,050
The auto repair shop

1200
01:36:05,560 --> 01:36:09,530
hello, what is it?

1201
01:36:09,940 --> 01:36:11,405
Is this the Tsuyama repair shop?

1202
01:36:12,190 --> 01:36:15,190
Hello, is Tsuyoshi Nishiyama there?

1203
01:36:16,371 --> 01:36:18,420
Eh, Tsuyoshi?

1204
01:36:23,383 --> 01:36:26,189
You know, He's just out for work right now

1205
01:36:27,434 --> 01:36:31,726
He's going to get the vehicle inspection for the Auto mobile.

1206
01:36:53,549 --> 01:36:55,181
I'm glad I made it in time,

1207
01:36:55,206 --> 01:36:56,110
thank you

1208
01:36:56,791 --> 01:36:58,400
Our Factory...

1209
01:36:59,058 --> 01:36:59,595
What's wrong?

1210
01:36:59,620 --> 01:37:01,116
Kayo,come.

1211
01:37:07,240 --> 01:37:09,282
send me a letter

1212
01:37:48,384 --> 01:37:49,806
Inoue-teacher.

1213
01:37:51,103 --> 01:37:53,275
What's wrong?

1214
01:38:04,900 --> 01:38:07,463
Mom,Teacher is here.

1215
01:38:11,181 --> 01:38:12,236
What's wrong?

1216
01:38:12,761 --> 01:38:19,329
She came on foot from the union.

1217
01:38:20,088 --> 01:38:23,205
She came on foot from the union.

1218
01:38:26,674 --> 01:38:28,650
Mom,Teacher is here.

1219
01:38:35,247 --> 01:38:45,025
Teacher,please take care of Tsuyoshi.

1220
01:38:47,134 --> 01:38:50,134
Ah, I see, I understand

1221
01:38:57,236 --> 01:38:58,322
hmm, the eldest son, huh?

1222
01:38:58,990 --> 01:39:00,706
So, how many family members are there?

1223
01:39:00,730 --> 01:39:01,166
Five

1224
01:39:03,946 --> 01:39:05,884
Well then, come right away starting today

1225
01:39:06,190 --> 01:39:07,266
Thank you in advance

1226
01:39:07,290 --> 01:39:07,856
Do a great job.

1227
01:39:09,455 --> 01:39:10,080
This.

1228
01:39:10,493 --> 01:39:11,059
Well then, I'm going home now

1229
01:39:11,260 --> 01:39:12,806
Yes, that's right

1230
01:39:13,810 --> 01:39:16,810
Oh, you're Ishiyama-kun, aren't you?

1231
01:39:16,970 --> 01:39:18,346
Phone call from the previous factory

1232
01:39:18,370 --> 01:39:20,525
Yes, I'm sorry

1233
01:39:20,660 --> 01:39:25,142
Hello, it's me

1234
01:39:26,990 --> 01:39:30,650
Huh, I just got a telegram now

1235
01:39:31,320 --> 01:39:33,026
I'm sorry.

1236
01:39:33,058 --> 01:39:37,392
Your mom has passed away, I'll read it again

1237
01:39:39,417 --> 01:39:41,759
Can you hear me?

1238
01:39:41,978 --> 01:39:44,705
Our mom is dead,Machie.

1239
01:39:45,197 --> 01:39:47,041
Can you hear me?

1240
01:39:48,205 --> 01:39:48,900
Yes

1241
01:39:49,111 --> 01:39:50,611
I'll hang up.

1242
01:40:00,415 --> 01:40:01,704
Is something wrong?

1243
01:40:02,120 --> 01:40:04,546
No, it's nothing

1244
01:40:04,570 --> 01:40:06,716
Then hurry up and bring your luggage

1245
01:40:06,740 --> 01:40:07,779
Yeah

1246
01:40:51,525 --> 01:40:53,455
Tsuyoshi is coming from today?

1247
01:40:53,900 --> 01:40:55,822
He's worried

1248
01:40:57,169 --> 01:40:59,103
Well, I suppose it's okay

1249
01:42:02,968 --> 01:42:04,337
They are practicing singing.

1250
01:42:04,362 --> 01:42:06,134
Is it already March?

1251
01:42:06,330 --> 01:42:08,689
It's been a year for us too.

1252
01:42:43,150 --> 01:42:44,416
Hey hurry up.

1253
01:42:44,939 --> 01:42:45,939
Reach.

1254
01:42:47,586 --> 01:42:48,941
How about this?

1255
01:42:48,994 --> 01:42:49,869
Reach.

1256
01:42:50,173 --> 01:42:51,966
Come on.

1257
01:42:52,963 --> 01:42:54,658
There's still a lot of chess left

1258
01:42:55,369 --> 01:42:56,580
I'm off to bed.

1259
01:42:57,405 --> 01:43:00,405
Hey, tomorrow you're the one who will boil the tea.

1260
01:43:07,102 --> 01:43:08,048
Hey Tsuyoshi

1261
01:43:09,009 --> 01:43:12,009
it would be nice if you went to bed too

1262
01:43:16,572 --> 01:43:17,845
Here it is.

1263
01:43:18,761 --> 01:43:20,220
oh, thank you

1264
01:43:36,580 --> 01:43:37,603
oh, is that you, Sensei?

1265
01:43:39,119 --> 01:43:40,392
Welcome.

1266
01:43:40,490 --> 01:43:41,931
I'm sorry for coming suddenly

1267
01:43:41,956 --> 01:43:43,025
Make a tea for him.

1268
01:43:43,050 --> 01:43:44,747
it's fine, it's fine

1269
01:43:53,993 --> 01:43:55,134
Tsuyoshi.

1270
01:44:00,002 --> 01:44:01,728
You saw the telegram, right?

1271
01:44:02,392 --> 01:44:03,174
Yes.

1272
01:44:04,588 --> 01:44:05,853
Why aren't you coming back?

1273
01:44:07,517 --> 01:44:12,580
Your mother died saying your name.

1274
01:44:13,804 --> 01:44:18,525
Forgive me....
I got a job here today.

1275
01:44:19,736 --> 01:44:21,377
I couldn't tell the factory manager about it.

1276
01:44:24,502 --> 01:44:26,166
I feel sorry for Mom.

1277
01:44:32,634 --> 01:44:36,213
I was afraid of losing my job.

1278
01:44:41,710 --> 01:44:44,536
What is it? Did you have something?

1279
01:44:44,560 --> 01:44:46,246
I was able to talk to the factory manager.

1280
01:45:00,149 --> 01:45:01,689
Bus has arrived

1281
01:45:16,199 --> 01:45:17,419
Thank you very much for coming.

1282
01:45:17,485 --> 01:45:18,325
Thanks for your hard work.

1283
01:45:18,350 --> 01:45:19,566
Welcome back.

1284
01:45:19,590 --> 01:45:20,804
It's cold, isn't it?

1285
01:45:21,650 --> 01:45:23,325
Tokyo is already fully in spring

1286
01:45:23,949 --> 01:45:25,011
Hmm, I guess so.

1287
01:45:29,510 --> 01:45:30,657
how was Kiyoshi?

1288
01:45:31,421 --> 01:45:33,339
The telegram has arrived there.

1289
01:45:34,606 --> 01:45:37,136
It was just about to get a job at Gonzo's factory

1290
01:45:37,900 --> 01:45:40,900
He thought that he shouldn't bring it up because it might ruin his job.

1291
01:45:42,040 --> 01:45:42,940
Oh, I see

1292
01:45:44,550 --> 01:45:47,550
They are doing their best in their own way

1293
01:45:50,780 --> 01:45:57,127
Principal, Let me be your employment officer again this year.

1294
01:45:58,623 --> 01:46:00,790
Please

1295
01:46:02,680 --> 01:46:03,433
Can you?

1296
01:46:03,520 --> 01:46:04,140
Yes.

1297
01:46:05,300 --> 01:46:06,393
Thank you very much.

1298
01:46:09,209 --> 01:46:10,096
Thank you very much.

1299
01:46:45,830 --> 01:46:49,195
Temporary employment train for Line 1 will depart

1300
01:46:51,554 --> 01:46:53,434
Please give my regard to the kids in Tokyo.

1301
01:46:54,526 --> 01:46:56,780
I'm counting on you again.

1302
01:46:59,248 --> 01:47:00,288
Have a safe trip.

1303
01:47:03,686 --> 01:47:05,697
Don't push yourself too hard.

1304
01:47:15,374 --> 01:47:17,340
I'll be off.

1305
01:48:10,165 --> 01:48:17,217
THE END

